problem:
Let  \[f(x) =
\begin{cases}
k(x) &\text{if }x>0, \\
x^4 - 4x^3 + 6x^2- 4x &\text{if }x\leq 0.
\end{cases}
\] Find the function $k(x)$ such that $f$ is its own inverse.
